        • Use OP Score to get a more accurate breakdown of your skill level.
        What is OP Score?
        A rating system that measures a users performance within a game by combining stats related to role, laning phase, kills / deaths / damage / wards / damage to objectives etc.
        Best Player Selection
        MVP
        The summoner that performed the best in the match
        ACE
        Best losing player, the summoner that performed the best for the losing team
        Feature
        The improved OP Score allows precise tracking of the user’s stats based on their play time. The OP Score is calculated every 5 minutes in ranked and regular games, and every 3 minutes in the Howling Abyss, allowing for a more detailed analysis of the player’s performance.
        Range of Scores
        0
        10
        For OP Score's beta test, based on the characteristics of each match your results may be somewhat inaccurate We will keep trying to improve the indicators and calculations used in OP Score so we can create the most objective rating possible. Please give us any feedback.
